OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fand mild in the east on Thursday, but
OL,7,Frain arriving further west.
OL,8,FTemperatures returning nearer to
OL,9,Faverage to end the week, with a
OL,10,Fmixture of cloud and sunny spells.
